Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Class TraditionalJSPParser

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp.TraditionalJSPParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
JSPParser
public class TraditionalJSPParser extends Object implements JSPParser
Parser for traditional JSP syntax using <% %> scriptlets and directives.

This parser handles JSP pages that use the classic JSP syntax with scriptlets, expressions, declarations, and directives. For example: 

 <%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" %>
 <%@ page import="java.util.*" %>
 <html>
 <body>
   <%-- JSP Comment --%>
   <% String message = "Hello, World!"; %>
   <h1><%= message %></h1>
   <%!
     private int counter = 0;
     public String getNextId() {
       return "id_" + (++counter);
     }
   %>
 </body>
 </html>
Author:
Chris Burdess
